The paper deals with brain extraction from medical images using a joint PCA image reconstruction approach. This involves modeling normal tissue appearance and pathologies, which is a common problem in medical image analysis. The paper also uses image registration and statistical modeling techniques. Given these factors, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and multimedia (cs.MM).
